<div id="review_45208496" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/45208496" />
    <a title="Bryce" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/1987923-bryce"><img alt="Bryce" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1442497859p2/1987923.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/45208496?book_show_action=true">Feb 02, 2009</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Bryce" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Bryce" href="/user/show/1987923-bryce">Bryce</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer45208496" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer7619694097395611717">My favorite Grisham, and I&apos;ve read almost all of them. He states in his own words that sometimes he gets &quot;a bit verbose&quot; - but I really liked it because of the depth that he goes into on the characters, which is mostly absent from his other stories.</span>
  <span id="freeText7619694097395611717" style="display:none">My favorite Grisham, and I've read almost all of them. He states in his own words that sometimes he gets "a bit verbose" - but I really liked it because of the depth that he goes into on the characters, which is mostly absent from his other stories.</span>
  <a data-text-id="7619694097395611717" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


